793e22d207688ff2","tid":1544470,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子殺人填命！"},{"pid":"193813062949145375399dceea926092254f8412","tid":1544470,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n好撚好聽<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWC2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=45bdaad0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗(<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"08f31575f641d907a10cdf93eef7661ee95a9d22","tid":1544470,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"佢想同大家分享一下防暴訓練最辛苦的環節:<br />\n<br />\n1. 防暴警察唔知示威者幾時出現，令到心理負擔好大。圍狗屋嘅話佢哋就可以坐喺冷氣房裏面指住你哋嚟笑。<br />\n<br />\n2. 示威者係狗屋附近四圍遊走，令防暴隊孭住全副武裝四圍跑，身水身汗。<br />\n<br />\n3. 示威者係狗屋附近四圍遊走，令防暴隊高層需要大量時間決定掃蕩邊一個區域的示威者， 當防暴隊去到嘅時候，又唔見人影，指揮官往往會以為自己決定出錯。<br />\n<br />\n4. 示威者係狗屋附近四圍遊走，令防暴隊喺街上逗留嘅時間越長，就越難分辨街坊同埋示威者，好有可能會誤中副車，射錯催淚彈，令到民意逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n5. 示威者係出咗催淚彈之後散曬，防暴隊終於可以返入去休息，呢一個時候示威者又出返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n呢位海軍提咗我哋幾樣嘢，希望大家以後心水清，唔好行去門口去送頭。<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得，防暴隊由收到call到決定推進，只需要三十分鐘之內。換言之只要圍咗30分鐘，就等於自行送頭<br />\n<br />\n希望呢位海軍可以畀大家一啲諗法，佢絕對唔支持大家咁樣玩<br />\n<br />\nSource:司徒小龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GavSzeto/posts/10159160892329062?__tn__=H-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGavSzeto%2Fposts%2F10159160892329062%3F__tn__%3DH-R&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWC2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d8e1b3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GavSzeto/posts/10159160892329062?__tn__=H-R</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－<br />\n注：上述意見乃已退役前英國皇家海軍意見，並不代表本人立場，本人僅是轉發意見，不支持任何的犯法行為。"},{"pid":"25100fc64fbc845e09b25657b7628f24c502aa72","tid":1544470,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2bed8e5497d1e38d3b0071d02223f97c24058e","tid":1544470,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e41de2442c7230f21ee53dac7832f8e4dcbabf","tid":1544470,"uid":187401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"我寧願炒車，聽日出嚟屌鳩我哋咒你哋死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,